##Description
This project is a web application that helps the customers to oder pizzas online from the store.


##Features
As a user of the application,you will be able to :

See a description of what type of pizzas offered .
Can make inquiry through a form.



##Requirements
Access to a computer or any other garget
Access to internet

##Installation Process
Clone to the repo : git clone https://github.com/Norah-coder/week4project.git

Unzip the downloaded files in a folder of choice.

Open the index file from the zipped file with any browser.
 
##Technology Used
HTML - which was used to develope the structure off the page.

CSS - which was used to style the User Interface.

JQUERY - which was used for DOM(Document Object Manipulation) scripts.



